title: Roofing Company In Florida Offering Free AR-15, Turkey With Purchase Of New Roof
description:
You butter believe this roofing company is all about that baste.

If you need a new roof you might as well kill two birds with one stone and get yourself a turkey and AR-15 because the owners of a Florida roofing company have announced its "Roof and Gobble" sale that is going on all month long.

The owners of Roof EZ, a roofing company located in Cape Coral, have announced a unique Thanksgiving special where anyone who purchases a roof during the month of November, will not only receive a free frozen turkey -- but also get a free AR-15.
